I’m so excited to finally let this cat out of the bag 💼 🐈 
I realized a dream of mine recently and that is to record some of my music with a producer who has made music that I’ve listened to obsessively. 
In October I flew down to LA and recorded an EP with the incredible Dougie Stu. 
It was an incredibly powerful experience. Surprisingly to me, A lot of old insecurities came up during the process. Thankfully I was treated incredibly kindly and warmly during these moments by Dougie and by myself and it felt very healing. Overall though, it was a really fun and inspiring and exciting. These songs got completely transformed and I am soooooo proud of them. 
The first song, Nesting is coming out December 9th at 9am. 
There is a link to presave the song on Spotify in my bio and I would super super appreciate it.
Also, all the music is now under my name! No more Needy Empty or Call me Daisy. 
So stay tuned friends ❤️❤️❤️
With love,
Ian
